description:
The word “peace” has become very popular nowadays. Although there is war, violence, mutual disrespect and sorrow, the dream of peace on earth is one that still inspires people to hold hands and work together. 
In this episode, we travel to Oslo, a city that has become e a world-wide symbol of peace on earth. Travel with us to see how Oslo and its people, including the Adventist community, are living and and sharing this peace with the rest of the world.
